data.title: Aarón Díaz Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Aarón Díaz with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

Moved to the U

S

as a child, but returned to Mexico for college

Was cast on the telenovela Clase 406 while he was still in acting school

Released his first album, Enamórate de mí, in 2009

Made his English-language acting debut in an episode of Pan Am in 2011

Was originally cast on Quantico in a recurring role for season 2, but was promoted to series regular before the season began
